data.description: Gorgeous Corner Lot Home in the popular Huntington Place Addition!  This all brick 3 Bedroom, 2 bath home offers an open floor plan w/custom features throughout - crown molding, tumbled stone backsplash, kitchen pantry w/ plenty of storage, granite counter tops, SS appliances, under cabinet lighting, ceramic floors in all wet areas and GE kitchen appliances. Master has double sink vanity, large walk in closet w/built in shelving, walk-in shower and tub. Large family room offers tray ceilings and gas log fire place. Back yard is completely fenced in with covered porch! Home includes ceiling fans in all rooms. New roof in 2022!  Come see!
